<br>
&quot;Now Luthair, move your hands and begin the chanting.&quot;<br>
&quot;Ok,&quot;<br>
Luthair was standing beside his mother attempting to raise a dead cat. So far he was failing miserably. He had absolutely no talent for magic. His parents hated him for it. He was born into the Moongazer family, a family solely composed of practitioners of the dark arts. Yet Luthair seemed to have absolutely no magical talent. Suddenly fractures creeped up the cat's bleaching bones. Then they exploded. Even though Luthair was at the point of the blast he was not hurt. His mother was. Her hands shook, as she stared at a shard of bone jutting out of her hand. There was going to be hell to pay.<br>
&quot;You miserable little wretch! Are you completely useless? This will teach you a lesson!&quot; with that she started to chant.<br>
Luthair convulsed as his blood scorched his veins. Rolling upon the ground clawing at his arms he finnaly worked up the strength to crawl to the bridge. At this point he could feel his own bodily fluids cauterizing themselves. Using his last ounce of strenght he rolled off the bridge. Despite the fact he was drowning, Luthair was releived by the icy waters. He nearly lost consciousness before he felt a hand coated in mail ringlets grab the back of his neck. Dragged spitting and splutering he expected to see the cruel face of one of Neriaks guards. Instead his saw a familiar face. That of his big sister Sidow. <br>
(Sidow 38th lvl Shadow Knight, Dark Elf, Lords of the Dark Realm, Bristlebane server) <br>
&quot;I see that you have annoyed mother again little brother,&quot; <br>
&quot;That I have,&quot; <br>
&quot;I'm guessing you will be sleeping among the roof tiles tonight.&quot;<br>
&quot;I will be,&quot;<br>
&quot;You can't use magic or swing a sword,&quot; what shall you become?&quot;<br>
&quot;I don't know,&quot;<br>
&quot;Well, you seem like you need some warming up, your shivering. Lets try and get you some ogre swill.&quot;<br>
&quot;That stuff tastes like it's name sake.&quot;<br>
&quot;You should be thankful that I'm making you an offer at all.&quot;<br>
&quot;Right you are!&quot;<br>
After the young Tier-dal had consumed the aptly named concoction  he thanked his older sister and decided to find his way up to the top of the building. Sleeping on the rooves of the city among the rats was safer than at home.<br>
Luthair woke with a start. He heard fighting. Crawling to the edge of the tiled roof he saw a small dark elf fighting a pair of ogres. Weaving in and out between them, the Tier-dal struck them down with his two knives. Luthair's eyes caught something. The Dark elf was wearing a mask of Ebony. Luthair knew what he was going to be. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=770.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=763.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.emailToFriend?topicID=769.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.threadControl?topicID=769.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=769.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=769.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thes